@page
@model Webority.Web.GovIndia.Pages.Services.CloudMeghrajModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "MeghRaj GI Cloud Services — Government Cloud & Managed Infrastructure";
    ViewData["Description"] = "Cloud deployment and managed services for Indian government on NIC National Data Centres and MeghRaj GI Cloud — 100% data in India, SLA-backed, DPDP Act compliant.";
    ViewData["ActiveNav"] = "services";
    ViewData["BodyClass"] = "services-page";
}
<!-- Hero -->
  <section class="egov-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="egov-hero-content">
        <h1>MeghRaj GI Cloud Services for Government India</h1>
        <p class="egov-hero-lead">Cloud deployment and managed services on NIC National Data Centres and MeghRaj GI Cloud — all data within India, SLA-backed, and DPDP Act compliant.</p>
        <p class="svc-hero-standards">100% Data in India   ·   MeghRaj &amp; NIC Certified   ·   24×7 SLA-Backed</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Deliver -->
  <section class="egov-band">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="egov-band-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="egov-eyebrow">What We Deliver</span>
          <h2 class="egov-h2">India’s Sovereign Cloud — Managed by Experts</h2>
          <p class="copy">We provide cloud deployment, infrastructure setup, and ongoing managed services for government applications — on NIC National Data Centres, MeghRaj GI Cloud, or approved private cloud. All government data remains within India.</p>
          <ul class="egov-checklist">
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Cloud architecture design &amp; deployment</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> MeghRaj / NIC-compatible hosting</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> DevOps, CI/CD pipeline implementation</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> 24×7 monitoring &amp; incident management</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Disaster Recovery &amp; Business Continuity</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Annual Maintenance Contracts with SLA</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> L1 / L2 / L3 helpdesk support</li>
            <li><span class="egov-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></span> Data localisation — DPDP Act compliant</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="egov-btn-row">
            <a asp-page="/Contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-glow btn-md"><span class="btn-glow-label">Discuss Your Requirements</span><svg class="btn-glow-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
            <a asp-page="/CaseStudies" class="btn btn-outline btn-md">View Projects</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="egov-ref-panel">
          <span class="egov-eyebrow">Reference Projects</span>
          <!-- TODO-WG: each public-sector reference below must have approved public listing before publishing. -->
          <ul class="egov-ref-list">
            <li class="egov-ref-item">
              <span class="egov-ref-logo egov-ref-logo--generic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="8" rx="2"/><rect x="2" y="14" width="20" height="8" rx="2"/><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="6.01" y2="6"/><line x1="6" y1="18" x2="6.01" y2="18"/></svg></span>
              <span>
                <p class="egov-ref-name">NIC National Data Centres</p>
                <p class="egov-ref-proj">Delhi · Hyderabad · Pune · Bhubaneswar</p>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="egov-ref-item">
              <span class="egov-ref-logo egov-ref-logo--generic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"/></svg></span>
              <span>
                <p class="egov-ref-name">MeghRaj GI Cloud</p>
                <p class="egov-ref-proj">Government of India’s sovereign cloud platform</p>
              </span>
            </li>
            <li class="egov-ref-item">
              <span class="egov-ref-logo egov-ref-logo--generic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></span>
              <span>
                <p class="egov-ref-name">Approved Private Cloud</p>
                <p class="egov-ref-proj">India-localised · DPDP Act compliant</p>
              </span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Capabilities -->
  <section class="egov-build">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="egov-build-head">
        <span class="egov-eyebrow">Capabilities</span>
        <h2 class="egov-h2">What Our Cloud &amp; Managed Services Deliver</h2>
        <p>Sovereign government cloud capability — no foreign server dependencies, no compliance gaps.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="egov-build-grid">
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M18 10h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 9 20h9a5 5 0 0 0 0-10z"/></svg></span>
          <h3>MeghRaj GI Cloud Architecture</h3>
          <p>End-to-end deployment on NIC National Data Centres and MeghRaj — fully sovereign, DPDP Act 2023 compliant, no AWS/Azure dependency.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"/><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Auto-Scaling for Citizen Load Spikes</h3>
          <p>Infrastructure that scales automatically during scheme launches, election portals, and national programme rollouts — zero downtime under load.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="6" y1="3" x2="6" y2="15"/><circle cx="18" cy="6" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="18" r="3"/><path d="M18 9a9 9 0 0 1-9 9"/></svg></span>
          <h3>CI/CD Pipelines for Government</h3>
          <p>Automated build, test, and deployment pipelines enabling secure, frequent releases without manual intervention or service disruption.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg></span>
          <h3>24×7 Uptime Monitoring &amp; SLA</h3>
          <p>Real-time application health monitoring, automated alerting, and L1/L2/L3 helpdesk with government-aligned SLA commitments.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-3-6.7L21 8"/><polyline points="21 3 21 8 16 8"/></svg></span>
          <h3>Disaster Recovery &amp; BCP</h3>
          <p>Geo-redundant backup, tested failover procedures, and business continuity planning — meeting ministry data retention requirements.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="egov-build-card">
          <span class="egov-build-ic" aria-hidden="true"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M14.7 6.3a4 4 0 0 0-5.4 5.4L3 18l3 3 6.3-6.3a4 4 0 0 0 5.4-5.4l-2.1 2.1-2.4-.6-.6-2.4z"/></svg></span>
          <h3>AMC &amp; Security Patch Management</h3>
          <p>Annual Maintenance Contracts with GIGW updates, security patches, dependency upgrades, and compliance reassessment every cycle.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Certifications -->
  <section class="egov-certs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sect-head">
        <span class="egov-eyebrow">Government &amp; Public Sector</span>
        <h2 class="egov-h2">Certifications</h2>
      </div>
      <!-- TODO-WG: confirm the exact list of held certifications; replace any seal below with the real certificate. -->
      <div class="cert-seals-row">
        <div class="cert-seal-card"><div class="cert-seal-img-wrap"><img class="cert-seal-img" src="/images/credentials/cmmi-l5.png" alt="CMMI Level 5 certified" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="cert-seal-card-name">CMMI Level 5</div></div>
        <div class="cert-seal-card"><div class="cert-seal-img-wrap"><img class="cert-seal-img" src="/images/credentials/iso-27001-2022.png" alt="ISO 27001:2022 certified" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="cert-seal-card-name">Information Security</div></div>
        <div class="cert-seal-card"><div class="cert-seal-img-wrap"><img class="cert-seal-img" src="/images/credentials/iso-9001-2015.png" alt="ISO 9001:2015 certified" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="cert-seal-card-name">Quality Management</div></div>
        <div class="cert-seal-card"><div class="cert-seal-img-wrap"><img class="cert-seal-img" src="/images/credentials/iso-20000-2018.png" alt="ISO 20000:2018 certified" loading="lazy" /></div><div class="cert-seal-card-name">IT Service Management</div></div>
        <div class="cert-seal-card"><div class="cert-seal-img-wrap"><img class="cert-seal-img" src="/images/logos/gov/Start up logo.svg" alt="DPIIT — Startup India recognised" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.parentNode.classList.add('reg-card-logo--fallback'); this.parentNode.setAttribute('aria-hidden','true'); this.parentNode.textContent='DPIIT';" /></div><div class="cert-seal-card-name">Startup India / DPIIT</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="egov-faq">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sect-head">

        <h2 class="egov-h2">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      <!-- TODO-WG: verify each Q&A pairing and all compliance/client claims (ISO version, certifications, named bodies) before publishing. -->
      <div class="faq-wrap">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">Does Webority deploy government platforms on MeghRaj GI Cloud and NIC Data Centres?</button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>MeghRaj GI Cloud (Government of India Cloud) is the Government of India’s sovereign cloud infrastructure managed by NIC. It is the mandated or preferred hosting environment for Central Ministry and State Government digital applications, ensuring 100% data sovereignty within India, compliance with DPDP Act 2023 data localisation requirements, and alignment with NIC information security policy. Webority provides specialist MeghRaj GI Cloud services including architecture design, deployment, and 24×7 managed services.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What are NIC National Data Centres and how does Webority use them?</button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>NIC National Data Centres (NDCs) are the Government of India’s sovereign Tier IV data centre facilities located in Delhi, Hyderabad, Pune, and Bhubaneswar. They provide the physical hosting for MeghRaj GI Cloud and direct NIC-hosted applications. Webority architects, deploys, and manages government applications on NIC NDC infrastructure — ensuring compliance with NIC information security policies, GoI data residency requirements, and DPDP Act 2023 obligations. All applications remain within Indian sovereign infrastructure with no dependency on foreign servers.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">What does a managed services AMC with Webority include for government applications?</button>
          <div class="faq-a"><p>Webority’s Annual Maintenance Contract (AMC) for government applications on MeghRaj GI Cloud or NIC infrastructure includes: 24×7 application monitoring and incident management, L1/L2/L3 tiered helpdesk with defined SLA response times, security patch management and version updates, Disaster Recovery and Business Continuity Planning (DR/BCP) testing, performance optimisation, and compliance documentation updates for annual GoI audits. All AMC engagements follow ITIL-aligned service management and align with government budget and payment cycles.</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA strip -->
  <section class="egov-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Moving to MeghRaj or NIC cloud?</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your application and its data classification — we’ll architect a sovereign, SLA-backed deployment.</p>
      <a asp-page="/Contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-glow btn-md"><span class="btn-glow-label">Contact Us</span><svg class="btn-glow-arrow" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="M13 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg></a>
    </div>
  </section>

@section HeadStyles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/pages/service-cloud.css" />
}
